{"tid":2042802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾30懲教富臨飯敍涉違令","createTime":"2020-05-30T04:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T05:53:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3b59398836f34e1482d779a724603ffc3193b4","tid":2042802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/JPJ6RU6OBI2YJDOXWDAZDVIGFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2FJPJ6RU6OBI2YJDOXWDAZDVIGFU%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=3382538c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2FJPJ6RU6OBI2YJDOXWDAZDVIGFU%2F&h=e86cef6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/JPJ6RU6OBI2YJDOXWDAZDVIGFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n逾30懲教富臨飯敍涉違令<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MQ3BRS3MVR2F3OEPWXXPRJQOHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMQ3BRS3MVR2F3OEPWXXPRJQOHI.jpg&h=7f951832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逾30名懲教人員在富臨酒家飯敍，涉違反限聚令。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】限聚令尚未結束，但有懲教署人員懷疑知法犯法。上周四逾30名懲教署人員為慶祝同事升職，在長沙灣廣場富臨漁港囍臨門酒家飯敍，其間多人打麻雀、飲酒及吸煙，涉違反限聚令，警員兩度到場均未檢控。懲教署回覆承認事件，指當晚屬休班人員私下飯敍，已轉介警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警兩次到場無檢控<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，本月21日逾30名隸屬小欖精神病治療中心的懲教署人員，疑無視限聚令，在長沙灣廣場富臨漁港囍臨門酒家飯敍，慶祝其中一人升職。其間所有人沒有佩戴口罩，在貴賓房。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆本報承認事件，指本月21日有休班懲教人員在長沙灣某酒家晚飯，屬私人性質，已將事件轉介其他執法機構跟進，強。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方指當晚接獲報案，稱長沙灣道一商場食肆內有人聚餐，餐桌分隔距離不足1.5米，疑違反限聚令，兩次派員到場，發現食肆內的餐桌分隔距離符合要求，每張餐桌沒有超過八名顧客，當日無人被捕或被票控。警方稱收到懲教署轉。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者何家朗"},{"pid":"a1ab7de8a31aaea23a32e4c1a6c3d83c5f38739c","tid":2042802,"uid":272912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"前線好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f900ec67d5416aefb868f1830a8870ba893d0c1a","tid":2042802,"uid":268342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"咁間酒樓，係咪一樣要告😎"},{"pid":"7d61868050529f8c8f2e41686d6eaa3e1c03f886","tid":2042802,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"邊個篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b0e803a83f767201d3f8403560314e5557b729","tid":2042802,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"懲教手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}